Alright.

47
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,020
But remember to eat.

48
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:21,700
Don't worry.

49
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:22,580
Tell you what,

50
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:23,860
I'll see you in the next day or two.

51
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:24,140
Okay.

52
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:24,540
Wait for me.

53
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:25,180
Okay.

54
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,860
Dinner's ready!

55
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:29,260
Let me get it.

56
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,900
Fish head... Hot!

57
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:33,860
Fish head and tofu soup.

58
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,060
Here you go.

59
00:02:38,540 --> 00:02:39,500
Have some more.

60
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,380
You made so much food.

61
