You should eat more.

64
00:02:45,260 --> 00:02:46,220
Look how thin you are.

65
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,100
Me gaining a bit of weight
isn't the issue.

66
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:49,620
It's

67
