we could set up a canopy?

228
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:10,260
If it does rain,

229
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:12,740
guests can shelter underneath.

230
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:13,700
If it's not raining

231
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:14,860
but very hot,

232
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:16,140
everyone can relax there in the shade.

233
00:09:16,700 --> 00:09:18,100
That's a brilliant idea.

234
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:20,220
Could you prepare some canopies for us?

235
00:09:20,220 --> 00:09:22,020
Just in case it rains.

236
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,060
Of course, Ms. Wen.

237
00:09:23,060 --> 00:09:24,180
That's absolutely no problem.

238
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:27,260
Inviting you along
was definitely the right call.

239
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,140
Hey, Zeyuan.

240
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,460
What have you been up to lately?

241
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:37,460
I started another new project.

242
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:38,740
Don't even think about it.

243
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:40,020
You always get screwed over
by your friends.

244
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:40,980
Haven't you learned your lesson?

245
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,060
Listen,

246
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:44,220
you've got to trust my vision on this.

247
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:44,820
Alright?

248
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:46,460
Keep it in mind for me.

249
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:47,820
Oh,

250
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:48,660
and one more thing.

251
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,460
Mom and Dad are visiting my place
in a couple of days.

252
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,460
Don't forget to come over for dinner.

253
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:53,620
Got it.

254
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:57,620
Shuhan,

255
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,300
do you prefer black or white?

256
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:01,220
What?

257
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:02,860
Never mind.

258
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:03,460
I'm hanging up.

259
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:09,460
That feels perfect.

260
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,620
Glad you like it.

261
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:11,500
That's the vibe.

262
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:13,060
Chinese and Western styles
can be separate.

263
00:10:15,540 --> 00:10:15,820
Yes.

264
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,780
Every wedding

265
00:10:17,780 --> 00:10:19,060
has a slogan.

266
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:21,300
Like something related to your names.

267
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,420
Like "Fortunate to Have Met You,
Warmth for a Lifetime."

268
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:25,060
Or do you have

269
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:27,340
any favorite romantic quotes?

270
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:28,420
We can think about it.

271
00:10:29,220 --> 00:10:32,340
♪Crumpled when held tight,
gone when you expand♪

272
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,100
Well...

273
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:35,860
I remember one.

274
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:39,060
Once, a boy told me,

275
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:40,740
"The moonlight is beautiful tonight."

276
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:44,500
And I like him too.

277
00:10:44,660 --> 00:10:45,780
So I replied,

278
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:47,580
"And the wind is gentle."

279
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:49,580
♪Occasional accidents sink
in someone's emotions♪

280
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:53,340
♪Who hasn't wondered if their life
would stay blank and bare?♪

281
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:54,140
That's quite romantic.

282
00:10:58,500 --> 00:10:59,020
This is

283
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:00,380
the final plan

284
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:01,620
we've settled on for now.

285
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:03,220
You can review the details.

